<item>
            <title>[LU-7933] debugfs stat reports invalid EA entry in inode</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7933</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Cannot get file extended attributes using debugfs stat command&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt; debugfs: stat fs68.lmf&lt;br/&gt;
 Inode: 139   Type: regular    Mode:  0644   Flags: 0x0&lt;br/&gt;
 Generation: 100269556    Version: 0x00000001:00000032&lt;br/&gt;
 User: 50304   Group:  1638   Size: 0&lt;br/&gt;
 File ACL: 0    Directory ACL: 0&lt;br/&gt;
 Links: 1   Blockcount: 0&lt;br/&gt;
 Fragment:  Address: 0    Number: 0    Size: 0&lt;br/&gt;
  ctime: 0x56f55e9f:00000000 &amp;#8211; Fri Mar 25 16:51:59 2016&lt;br/&gt;
  atime: 0x5582a136:00000000 &amp;#8211; Thu Jun 18 12:45:10 2015&lt;br/&gt;
  mtime: 0x5582a136:00000000 &amp;#8211; Thu Jun 18 12:45:10 2015&lt;br/&gt;
 crtime: 0x56f55e9f:7b34df44 &amp;#8211; Fri Mar 25 16:51:59 2016&lt;br/&gt;
 Size of extra inode fields: 28&lt;br/&gt;
 Extended attributes stored in inode body:&lt;br/&gt;
 invalid EA entry in inode&lt;br/&gt;
 BLOCKS:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BTW, extended attributes are correctly reported by a former e2fsprogs version (&amp;lt;1.42.13.wc3)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Extended attributes stored in inode body:&lt;br/&gt;
  lma = &quot;00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 04 00 c0 02 00 00 00 0b 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 &quot; (24)&lt;br/&gt;
  lma: fid=[0x2c0000400:0xb:0x0] compat=0 incompat=0&lt;br/&gt;
  lov = &quot;d0 0b d1 0b 01 00 00 00 0b 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 04 00 c0 02 00 00 00 00 00 10 00 01 00 00 00 04 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 02 00 00 00&quot; (56)&lt;br/&gt;
  link = &quot;df f1 ea 11 01 00 00 00 32 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 0 00 00 00 1a 00 00 00 02 c0 00 04 00 00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00 66 73 36 38 2e 6c 6d 66 &quot; (50)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

